Time\">SpaceTime</a> → <a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsVec\">HiggsVec</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a `HiggsField`, the corresponding map from `SpaceTime` to `HiggsVec`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField.toHiggsVec","kind":"def","line":533,"name":"StandardModel.HiggsField.toHiggsVec","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L533-L534"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField.const_apply\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">HiggsField</span>.<span class=\"name\">const_apply</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">φ</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsVec\">HiggsVec</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/SpaceAndTime/SpaceTime/Basic.html#SpaceTime\">SpaceTime</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField.const\">const</a> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">x</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">φ</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"For all spacetime points, the constant Higgs field defined by a Higgs vector,\nreturns that Higgs Vector. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField.const_apply","kind":"theorem","line":522,"name":"StandardModel.HiggsField.const_apply","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L522-L525"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField.const\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">HiggsField</span>.<span class=\"name\">const</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsVec\">HiggsVec</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/LinearMap/Defs.html#LinearMap\">→ₗ[</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Real/Basic.html#Real\">ℝ</a><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Module/LinearMap/Defs.html#LinearMap\">]</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField\">HiggsField</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Given a vector in `HiggsVec` the constant Higgs field with value equal to that\nsection. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField.const","kind":"def","line":506,"name":"StandardModel.HiggsField.const","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L506-L520"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">HiggsField</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The type `HiggsField` is defined such that elements are smooth sections of the trivial\nvector bundle `HiggsBundle`. Such elements are Higgs fields. Since `HiggsField` is\ntrivial as a vector bundle, a Higgs field is equivalent to a smooth map\nfrom `SpaceTime` to `HiggsVec`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsField","kind":"def","line":482,"name":"StandardModel.HiggsField","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L482-L487"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.instContMDiffVectorBundleTopWithTopENatRealSpaceTimeOfNatNatHiggsVecHiggsBundleVectorAsSmoothManifold\"><span class=\"name\">StandardModel</span>.<span class=\"name\">instContMDiffVectorBundleTopWithTopENatRealSpaceTimeOfNatNatHiggsVecHiggsBundleVectorAsSmoothManifold</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/VectorBundle/Basic.html#ContMDiffVectorBundle\">ContMDiffVectorBundle</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Order/Notation.html#Top.top\">⊤</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsVec\">HiggsVec</a> <a href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsBundle\">HiggsBundle</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./PhysLean/Relativity/Tensors/RealTensor/Vector/Basic.html#Lorentz.Vector.asSmoothManifold\">Lorentz.Vector.asSmoothManifold</a> <span class=\"fn\">3</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The instance of a smooth vector bundle with total space `HiggsBundle` and fiber `HiggsVec`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.instContMDiffVectorBundleTopWithTopENatRealSpaceTimeOfNatNatHiggsVecHiggsBundleVectorAsSmoothManifold","kind":"instance","line":468,"name":"StandardModel.instContMDiffVectorBundleTopWithTopENatRealSpaceTimeOfNatNatHiggsVecHiggsBundleVectorAsSmoothManifold","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L468-L470"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/Particles/StandardModel/HiggsBoson/Basic.html#StandardModel.HiggsBundle\"><span class=\"name\">StandardMode